reviewText: Great movies. Nice to get them together in the same box. Speed Service too :)

I haven't even finished watching it. I had sold my original, first run copies of The Watchmen several years ago so thought it would be nice to revisit the original. But the way it is presented here just doesn't work for me. But I'm not disputing that it is liked by others. It's just a matter of taste.
A great way to experience one of the greatest  comic books ever written.
Not what i thought it would be
This is a very nice movie that would be appreciated by mature adults.

The 6 hour motion comic takes everything from the graphic novel and animates the story to motion. If you have never read or finished the novel, it is a great way to view the complete story of the watchmen.
